{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.1","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:1","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.028.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Offrandes volontaires pour le temple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. 1 Ch 22:2-5, 14-19. Ex 35:4, etc. (2 Co 8:3-5; 9:7. Ph 4:17.) Ro 12:8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Le roi David dit \u00e0 toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e: Mon fils Salomon, le seul que Dieu ait choisi, est jeune et d\u2019un \u00e2ge faible, et l\u2019ouvrage est consid\u00e9rable, car ce palais n\u2019est pas pour un homme, mais il est pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.2","name":"1 Chroniques 29:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.28.21","name":"1 Chroniques 28:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.28.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.2","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:2","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>J\u2019ai mis toutes mes forces \u00e0 pr\u00e9parer pour la maison de mon Dieu de l\u2019or pour ce qui doit \u00eatre d\u2019or, de l\u2019argent pour ce qui doit \u00eatre d\u2019argent, de l\u2019airain pour ce qui doit \u00eatre d\u2019airain, du fer pour ce qui doit \u00eatre de fer, et du bois pour ce qui doit \u00eatre de bois, des pierres d\u2019onyx et des pierres \u00e0 ench\u00e2sser, des pierres brillantes et de diverses couleurs, toutes sortes de pierres pr\u00e9cieuses, et du marbre blanc en quantit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.3","name":"1 Chroniques 29:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.1","name":"1 Chroniques 29:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.3","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:3","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>De plus, dans mon attachement pour la maison de mon Dieu, je donne \u00e0 la maison de mon Dieu l\u2019or et l\u2019argent que je poss\u00e8de en propre, outre tout ce que j\u2019ai pr\u00e9par\u00e9 pour la maison du sanctuaire:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.4","name":"1 Chroniques 29:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.2","name":"1 Chroniques 29:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.4","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:4","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>trois mille talents d\u2019or, d\u2019or d\u2019Ophir, et sept mille talents d\u2019argent \u00e9pur\u00e9, pour en rev\u00eatir les parois des b\u00e2timents,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.5","name":"1 Chroniques 29:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.3","name":"1 Chroniques 29:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.5","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:5","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>l\u2019or pour ce qui doit \u00eatre d\u2019or, et l\u2019argent pour ce qui doit \u00eatre d\u2019argent, et pour tous les travaux qu\u2019ex\u00e9cuteront les ouvriers. Qui veut encore pr\u00e9senter volontairement aujourd\u2019hui ses offrandes \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.6","name":"1 Chroniques 29:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.4","name":"1 Chroniques 29:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.6","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:6","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Les chefs des maisons paternelles, les chefs des tribus d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, les chefs de milliers et de centaines, et les intendants du roi firent volontairement des offrandes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.7","name":"1 Chroniques 29:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.5","name":"1 Chroniques 29:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.7","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:7","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ils donn\u00e8rent pour le service de la maison de Dieu cinq mille talents d\u2019or, dix mille dariques, dix mille talents d\u2019argent, dix-huit mille talents d\u2019airain, et cent mille talents de fer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.8","name":"1 Chroniques 29:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.6","name":"1 Chroniques 29:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.8","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:8","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ceux qui poss\u00e9daient des pierres les livr\u00e8rent pour le tr\u00e9sor de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel entre les mains de Jehiel, le Guerschonite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.9","name":"1 Chroniques 29:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.7","name":"1 Chroniques 29:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.9","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:9","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Le peuple se r\u00e9jouit de leurs offrandes volontaires, car c\u2019\u00e9tait avec un c\u0153ur bien dispos\u00e9 qu\u2019ils les faisaient \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel; et le roi David en eut aussi une grande joie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.10","name":"1 Chroniques 29:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.8","name":"1 Chroniques 29:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.10","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:10","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Pri\u00e8re de David<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-19: cf. (N\u00e9 9:5, 6. Mt 6:13. Ro 11:36.) Ps 145.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>David b\u00e9nit l\u2019\u00c9ternel en pr\u00e9sence de toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e. Il dit: B\u00e9ni sois-tu, d\u2019\u00e9ternit\u00e9 en \u00e9ternit\u00e9, \u00c9ternel, Dieu de notre p\u00e8re Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.11","name":"1 Chroniques 29:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.9","name":"1 Chroniques 29:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.11","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:11","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>A toi, \u00c9ternel, la grandeur, la force et la magnificence, l\u2019\u00e9ternit\u00e9 et la gloire, car tout ce qui est au ciel et sur la terre t\u2019appartient; \u00e0 toi, \u00c9ternel, le r\u00e8gne, car tu t\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ves souverainement au-dessus de tout!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.12","name":"1 Chroniques 29:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.10","name":"1 Chroniques 29:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.12","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:12","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>C\u2019est de toi que viennent la richesse et la gloire, c\u2019est toi qui domines sur tout, c\u2019est dans ta main que sont la force et la puissance, et c\u2019est ta main qui a le pouvoir d\u2019agrandir et d\u2019affermir toutes choses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.13","name":"1 Chroniques 29:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.11","name":"1 Chroniques 29:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.13","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:13","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Maintenant, \u00f4 notre Dieu, nous te louons, et nous c\u00e9l\u00e9brons ton nom glorieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.14","name":"1 Chroniques 29:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.12","name":"1 Chroniques 29:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.14","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:14","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Car qui suis-je et qui est mon peuple, pour que nous puissions te faire volontairement ces offrandes? Tout vient de toi, et nous recevons de ta main ce que nous t\u2019offrons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.15","name":"1 Chroniques 29:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.13","name":"1 Chroniques 29:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.15","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:15","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Nous sommes devant toi des \u00e9trangers et des habitants, comme tous nos p\u00e8res; nos jours sur la terre sont comme l\u2019ombre, et il n\u2019y a point d\u2019esp\u00e9rance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.16","name":"1 Chroniques 29:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.14","name":"1 Chroniques 29:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.16","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:16","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, c\u2019est de ta main que viennent toutes ces richesses que nous avons pr\u00e9par\u00e9es pour te b\u00e2tir une maison, \u00e0 toi, \u00e0 ton saint nom, et c\u2019est \u00e0 toi que tout appartient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.17","name":"1 Chroniques 29:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.15","name":"1 Chroniques 29:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.17","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:17","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Je sais, \u00f4 mon Dieu, que tu sondes le c\u0153ur, et que tu aimes la droiture; aussi je t\u2019ai fait toutes ces offrandes volontaires dans la droiture de mon c\u0153ur, et j\u2019ai vu maintenant avec joie ton peuple qui se trouve ici t\u2019offrir volontairement ses dons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.18","name":"1 Chroniques 29:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.16","name":"1 Chroniques 29:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.18","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:18","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>\u00c9ternel, Dieu d\u2019Abraham, d\u2019Isaac et d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, nos p\u00e8res, maintiens \u00e0 toujours dans le c\u0153ur de ton peuple ces dispositions et ces pens\u00e9es, et affermis son c\u0153ur en toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.19","name":"1 Chroniques 29:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.17","name":"1 Chroniques 29:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.19","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:19","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Donne \u00e0 mon fils Salomon un c\u0153ur d\u00e9vou\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019observation de tes commandements, de tes pr\u00e9ceptes et de tes lois, afin qu\u2019il mette en pratique toutes ces choses, et qu\u2019il b\u00e2tisse le palais pour lequel j\u2019ai fait des pr\u00e9paratifs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.20","name":"1 Chroniques 29:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.18","name":"1 Chroniques 29:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.20","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:20","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-25: cf. 1 R 8:62-66. (1 R 1:33-39. 2 Ch 1:1.) Ps 72.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>David dit \u00e0 toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e: B\u00e9nissez l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu! Et toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e b\u00e9nit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res. Ils s\u2019inclin\u00e8rent et se prostern\u00e8rent devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel et devant le roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.21","name":"1 Chroniques 29:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.19","name":"1 Chroniques 29:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.21","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:21","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Le lendemain de ce jour, ils offrirent en sacrifice et en holocauste \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel mille taureaux, mille b\u00e9liers et mille agneaux, avec les libations ordinaires, et d\u2019autres sacrifices en grand nombre pour tout Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.22","name":"1 Chroniques 29:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.20","name":"1 Chroniques 29:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.22","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:22","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Ils mang\u00e8rent et burent ce jour-l\u00e0 devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel avec une grande joie, ils proclam\u00e8rent roi pour la seconde fois Salomon, fils de David, ils l\u2019oignirent devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel comme chef, et ils oignirent Tsadok comme sacrificateur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.23","name":"1 Chroniques 29:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.21","name":"1 Chroniques 29:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.23","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:23","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Salomon s\u2019assit sur le tr\u00f4ne de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, comme roi \u00e0 la place de David, son p\u00e8re. Il prosp\u00e9ra, et tout Isra\u00ebl lui ob\u00e9it.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.24","name":"1 Chroniques 29:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.22","name":"1 Chroniques 29:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.24","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:24","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Tous les chefs et les h\u00e9ros, et m\u00eame tous les fils du roi David se soumirent au roi Salomon.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.25","name":"1 Chroniques 29:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.23","name":"1 Chroniques 29:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.25","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:25","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e9leva au plus haut degr\u00e9 Salomon sous les yeux de tout Isra\u00ebl, et il rendit son r\u00e8gne plus \u00e9clatant que ne fut celui d\u2019aucun roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl avant lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.26","name":"1 Chroniques 29:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.24","name":"1 Chroniques 29:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.26","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:26","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.027,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Sa mort<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 26-30: cf. (2 S 23:1-5. 1 R 2:10-12.) Ac 13:36.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>David, fils d\u2019Isa\u00ef, r\u00e9gna sur tout Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.27","name":"1 Chroniques 29:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.25","name":"1 Chroniques 29:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.27","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:27","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Le temps qu\u2019il r\u00e9gna sur Isra\u00ebl fut de quarante ans: \u00e0 H\u00e9bron il r\u00e9gna sept ans, et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem il r\u00e9gna trente-trois ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.28","name":"1 Chroniques 29:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.26","name":"1 Chroniques 29:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.28","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:28","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Il mourut dans une heureuse vieillesse, rassasi\u00e9 de jours, de richesse et de gloire. Et Salomon, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.27","name":"1 Chroniques 29:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.29","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:29","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Chr.029.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Les actions du roi David, les premi\u00e8res et les derni\u00e8res, sont \u00e9crites dans le livre de Samuel le voyant, dans le livre de Nathan le proph\u00e8te, et dans le livre de Gad le proph\u00e8te,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.30","name":"1 Chroniques 29:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.28","name":"1 Chroniques 29:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.30","label":"","reference":"1 Chroniques 29:30","prev_osis_id":"1Chr.029.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Chr.29.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>avec tout son r\u00e8gne et tous ses exploits, et ce qui s\u2019est pass\u00e9 de son temps, soit en Isra\u00ebl, soit dans tous les royaumes des autres pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.1.1","name":"2 Chroniques 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Chr.29.29","name":"1 Chroniques 29:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Chr.29.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc16c3d18.37089929');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc16c3d18.37089929\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc16c3d18.37089929","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc16c3d18.37089929'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc16c3d18.37089929\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}